---
import DlcLayout from "../../layouts/DlcLayout.astro";
import QuestStep from "../../components/QuestStep.astro";
import Image from "../../components/Image.astro";
import Tip from "../../components/Tip.astro";
import EndLogo from "../../components/EndLogo.astro";
import MediaGrid from "../../components/MediaGrid.astro";

const baseUrl = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;

const sections = [
  { id: "old-city", label: "Old City" },
  { id: "northwestern-island", label: "Northwestern Island" },
  { id: "northeastern-island", label: "Northeastern Island" },
  { id: "southeastern-island", label: "Southeastern Island" },
  { id: "southwestern-island", label: "Southwestern Island" },
];
---

<DlcLayout
  title="World Exploration"
  subtitle="DLC WALKTHROUGH"
  guideId="dlc-world-exploration"
  sections={sections}
>
  <!-- SECTION 1: Old City -->
  <section id="old-city" class="content-section">
    <h2>Old City</h2>

    <p>
      Since we can now use our airship, let's explore the world, at least what
      we can right now. Of course, before we do the whole exploration with the
      airship, let's go explore the Old City. Remember the entrance I mentioned
      at the end of the Deadlands? Let's go there.
    </p>

    <p>
      If you don't remember where it is, fast travel to the northwestern
      teleportation crystal and go right from it and around and you'll see a
      hidden path going into the side of the cliff.
    </p>

    <MediaGrid columns={2}>
      <Image
        src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/a/ad/Ec_931.jpg/363px-Ec_931.jpg"
        alt="Hidden path entrance in the cliff"
      />
      <Image
        src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/d/d6/Ec_932.jpg/363px-Ec_932.jpg"
        alt="Path leading into the Old City"
      />
    </MediaGrid>

    <p>
      Inside follow the path and go down to the bottom of the cave where you'll
      enter the Old City.
    </p>

    <p>
      In here go right, kill the Phantom Pains and jump down the wall. At the
      bottom we can go left or right. Go left and jump down the ledge in the
      bottom left corner to reach a chest that has <strong
        >Mythical Skull x4</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/6/69/Ec_934.jpg/600px-Ec_934.jpg"
      alt="Chest with Mythical Skull x4"
    />

    <p>
      Jump down and enter the building to the right of the stairs. Go through
      the building and back outside go left to find a chest with <strong
        >Evasion Master</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/3/3b/Ec_935.jpg/600px-Ec_935.jpg"
      alt="Chest with Evasion Master"
    />

    <p>
      Head to the far right now and enter the building. Go through this one as
      well and at the end you can find a chest with <strong
        >Vanyard's String x4</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/0/0d/Ec_936.jpg/600px-Ec_936.jpg"
      alt="Chest with Vanyard's String x4"
    />

    <p>
      That's all we can explore on this side. Return across the last 2 buildings
      then enter the upper left building (in front of where you first jumped
      down the ledge). Inside, go inside the first room to find a chest with <strong
        >Evasionist</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/e/e3/Ec_933.jpg/600px-Ec_933.jpg"
      alt="Chest with Evasionist"
    />

    <p>
      Go right now and down the stairs and exit the building. Out here go down 2
      sets of stairs. At the bottom go right first and around to find a <strong
        >Pool of Power</strong
      >. These are ALWAYS welcome.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/f/fb/Ec_937.jpg/600px-Ec_937.jpg"
      alt="Pool of Power location"
    />

    <p>
      Take the left path now and at the bottom, on the southern side you'll see
      a hole you can jump down into. Do so and you'll find a cave with a
      teleportation crystal. If you go north you'll see platform with 4 colored
      crystals. What is this place? This screams boss fight!
    </p>

    <p>
      There's nothing we can do and we're pretty much done exploring... right
      now at least.
    </p>

    <p>
      Go ahead and call your airship now and we'll be able to move around. Let's
      do this.
    </p>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 2: Northwestern Island -->
  <section id="northwestern-island" class="content-section">
    <h2>Northwestern Island</h2>

    <p>You can find this one northwest of Deadlands.</p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/1/1a/Ec_938.jpg/600px-Ec_938.jpg"
      alt="Northwestern Island location"
    />

    <p>
      Once we land, get on your Sky Armor and go to the larger island to the
      northeast. Get off here and open the large golden chest for <strong
        >Flesh of Farnese</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/f/ff/Ec_939.jpg/600px-Ec_939.jpg"
      alt="Golden chest with Flesh of Farnese"
    />
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 3: Northeastern Island -->
  <section id="northeastern-island" class="content-section">
    <h2>Northeastern Island</h2>

    <p>This one is located northeast of the Wastelands.</p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/b/b5/Ec_940.jpg/600px-Ec_940.jpg"
      alt="Northeastern Island location"
    />

    <p>
      As you land, directly south you can find a <strong>Fishing Spot</strong>,
      and to the right is a Worm Merchant to sell you materials for all your
      upgrading needs.
    </p>

    <MediaGrid columns={2}>
      <Image
        src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/e/e4/Ec_941.jpg/363px-Ec_941.jpg"
        alt="Fishing Spot on Northeastern Island"
      />
      <Image
        src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/3/3f/Ec_942.jpg/363px-Ec_942.jpg"
        alt="Worm Merchant on Northeastern Island"
      />
    </MediaGrid>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 4: Southeastern Island -->
  <section id="southeastern-island" class="content-section">
    <h2>Southeastern Island</h2>

    <p>This is south of the Wastelands.</p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/f/f8/Ec_943.jpg/600px-Ec_943.jpg"
      alt="Southeastern Island location"
    />

    <p>
      Once here head take the northwestern path. Take this north and around the
      island. You'll eventually reach a chest at the very end with <strong
        >Queen's Gun</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/c/cd/Ec_944.jpg/600px-Ec_944.jpg"
      alt="Chest with Queen's Gun"
    />

    <p>
      From here use the lip to jump down to the little island below so you can
      get back on your Sky Armors. Get off where we started, head north and
      you'll need to fight some cat enemies. After fighting them, take the
      northeastern ladder and up here go right to find a chest with <strong
        >Lankintin Star</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/2/2a/Ec_945.jpg/600px-Ec_945.jpg"
      alt="Chest with Lankintin Star"
    />

    <p>
      Go left now then take the UPPER path first to find a chest with <strong
        >Robes Bonus</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/9/92/Ec_946.jpg/600px-Ec_946.jpg"
      alt="Chest with Robes Bonus"
    />

    <p>
      Go ahead and take the bottom path. You'll be able to jump from platform to
      platform. Follow this path until you reach yet another fork. Once again,
      take the top path first to reach a chest with <strong
        >Lankintin Star</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/2/22/Ec_947.jpg/600px-Ec_947.jpg"
      alt="Chest with second Lankintin Star"
    />

    <p>
      Return and take the bottom path next. Go up the ladders and take this path
      until you see 2 lips you can use to jump off. Take the RIGHT GREEN one to
      reach a <strong>Pool of Power</strong>.
    </p>

    <MediaGrid columns={2}>
      <Image
        src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/1/1d/Ec_948.jpg/363px-Ec_948.jpg"
        alt="Platform with colored lips"
      />
      <Image
        src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/e/e5/Ec_949.jpg/363px-Ec_949.jpg"
        alt="Pool of Power on Southeastern Island"
      />
    </MediaGrid>

    <p>And with that we're done with this place.</p>
  </section>

  <!-- SECTION 5: Southwestern Island -->
  <section id="southwestern-island" class="content-section">
    <h2>Southwestern Island</h2>

    <p>This one is southwest of the Deadlands.</p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/9/9f/Ec_950.jpg/600px-Ec_950.jpg"
      alt="Southwestern Island location"
    />

    <p>
      Once here fly directly north to find a green island. Get off on the
      eastern side of it, go west and kill the cat enemies. Afterwards, check
      the southern side to find a <strong>Fishing Spot</strong>.
    </p>

    <MediaGrid columns={2}>
      <Image
        src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/8/8c/Ec_952.jpg/363px-Ec_952.jpg"
        alt="Green island on Southwestern Island"
      />
      <Image
        src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/6/68/Ec_953.jpg/363px-Ec_953.jpg"
        alt="Fishing Spot on Southwestern Island"
      />
    </MediaGrid>

    <p>
      Go further left to find a chest with <strong>Lankintin Star x2</strong>.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/9/9e/Ec_951.jpg/600px-Ec_951.jpg"
      alt="Chest with Lankintin Star x2"
    />

    <p>
      Go ahead and use the lip here to jump down to another chest, this one with <strong
        >Collector's Coin</strong
      >.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/7/7a/Ec_954.jpg/600px-Ec_954.jpg"
      alt="Chest with Collector's Coin"
    />

    <p>
      From here jump down to the south, call in your Sky Armors and head back to
      the green island up above, but from here you'll want to go northeast to
      find a second green island. Get off on the southwestern corner and follow
      the path to the very end to find a chest with <strong>Ambrosia</strong>.
    </p>

    <Image
      src="https://cdn.staticneo.com/ew/thumb/b/b9/Ec_955.jpg/600px-Ec_955.jpg"
      alt="Chest with Ambrosia"
    />
  </section>

  <EndLogo />
</DlcLayout>

<style>
  .content-section {
    padding: 2rem 0;
  }

  .content-section h2 {
    color: var(--accent-gold);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-color);
    padding-bottom: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 2rem);
    text-shadow: 0 2px 4px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
  }
</style>
